doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    title URL Shortener Microservice - Nicholas Asimov
    link(href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootswatch/3.3.6/flatly/bootstrap.min.css", rel="stylesheet", integrity="sha384-XYCjB+hFAjSbgf9yKUgbysEjaVLOXhCgATTEBpCqT1R3jvG5LGRAK5ZIyRbH5vpX", crossorigin="anonymous")
  body
    .container
      .test
        h1(style="margin-bottom: 15px;") API Basejump: URL Shortener Microservice
        p Written by: #[a(href="https://www.freecodecamp.com/nicholasasimov") Nicholas Asimov]

        blockquote
          h3 User stories
          ol
            li I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.
            li If I pass an invalid URL that doesn't follow the valid http://www.example.com format, the JSON response will contain an error instead.
            li When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link.

        h3 Example creation usage
        code https://reducer.herokuapp.com/new/http://www.example.com
          br
        code https://reducer.herokuapp.com/new/http://example.com

        h3 Example creation output
        code { "original_url":"http://www.example.com", "short_url":"https://reducer.herokuapp.com/3682" }

        h3 Usage
        code https://reducer.herokuapp.com/3682
        span &nbsp;will redirect to:&nbsp;
        code http://www.example.com
